式的角色，你不能否认有些可爱的特质，但是只要是清醒的人都明白其中的边缘性，你要是跟我用智障正确来争论，用什么啊普通人也有大智慧，边缘人也有大作为这种揣着明白装糊涂的观点来杠，我不理你，有魅力这个描述要是看不懂，就想想那个角色你会不会去追他和他喜结连理。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-7e5407d3ad8e08a49d61bbced61d35dc_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/486092829"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIkuWi3oCtpq1JEAMaCDcwMzAyMTk2II7w7okGMAY4ekAncgk0ODYwOTI4Mjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1633493345.701172", "card_id": "Q_474123071", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 139}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人在什么情况下才能大彻大悟？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-62449aeb120c9005d4b857e2bde78c43_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/474123071"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkuWi3oCtpq1JEAMaCDY3NjQwNzA4IKCP6IcGMAQ43ANAKHIJNDc0MTIzMDcxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1633493345.7015529", "card_id": "Q_475558897", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 71}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价影视作品《五个扑水的少年》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-711eccc83c0c514b73d085fde0e156c8_720w.jpg?source=2044ae36"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/475558897"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IkuWi3oCtpq1JEAMaCDY3OTYwMTg3IJDqg4gGMAM4dkApcgk0NzU1NTg4OTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1633493345.7019157", "card_id": "Q_420838577", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 122}, "target"